title: Bookface Cafe
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Organic, Western, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Small coffee shop and deli attached to Bookends bookshop in Pacific Fair shopping complex. Typically offers at least 3 vegan choices for sweets, such as vegan cheesecake, chocolate peppermint squares, and power balls. Offers other vegetarian cakes and slices and salad sandwiches/wraps as well as coffee and tea with soy milk and other milks.
streetAddress: Pacific Fair Shopping Centre, Hooker Blvd, Mermaid Beach
